<HEADLINE> Albania Urges Compromise Among Kosovo Parties </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, December 8 (Xinhua) -- Albanian President Rexhep
Meidani has appealed for compromise and coordination among
Kosovo's ethnic Albanian parties in dealing with Belgrade.
</P>
<P>
Meeting with Rifat Blaku, deputy-chairman of the Kosovo
Parliamentary Party, on Monday, Meidani said Albania will try its
best to attain a fair settlement to the Kosovo issue.
</P>
<P>
