China will take on South Korea, which downed Thailand in the
quarter-finals.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong of China beat Iran 5-0 in the first round, sailing
into the quarter-finals to face the defending champion Indonesia
on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
In the women's section, South Korea edged out Chinese Taipei
3-2 while Indonesia whitewashed Malaysia 5-0. The winning sides
secured their semi-final berths.
</P>
<P>
China meets Hong Kong, China, and Japan faces Thailand in the
other half of the quarter-finals on Wednesday. 
</P>
