<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 8 (Xinhua) -- Fu Quanyou, chief of the
general staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA), met
here today with Charles Freeman, former U.S. Assistant Secretary
of Defense for International Security, and his party.
</P>
<P>
Charles Freeman is a sinologist who accompanied President
Richard Nixon on the historic China trip as an interpreter and
served as deputy chief of mission at the US embassy to China in
the 1980s.
</P>
<P>
