in international and regional security that has increased the
common ground and reduced the differences between them and gave an
account of China's defense policy and military development.
</P>
<P>
Freeman said that the people of both countries are truly
delighted at the smooth progress in Sino-U.S. relations, and he
strongly recommended that bilateral cooperation and exchanges be
increased to reduce differences in viewpoints between the two
countries caused by divergences in their culture, traditions and
other fields.
</P>
<P>
