6.82 seconds ahead of the 20-year-old Wu and 7.40 faster than
Chinese Chen Yan, the world record holder over 400m.
</P>
<P>
Wu set the world record of 2:09.72 and won the 200m individual
medley title in the world championships in Perth, Australia, in
January. 
