<HEADLINE> Myanmar Seizes Counterfeit Thai Baht Notes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, December 8 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar authorities have seized
some 887 counterfeit 500 Thai baht notes in illegal trade at the
border town of Tachilek, eastern Shan state, opposite Thailand's
Maesai.
</P>
