<HEADLINE> IDB Approves Loan for Guatemala's Agriculture Sector </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 7 (Xinhua) -- The Inter-American
Development Bank (IDB) Monday announced the approval of a 33
million U.S. dollar loan for Guatemala's restructuring of food and
agriculture production.
</P>
