said 10 ambulances, three fire-fighting appliances and a rescue
vehicle had also been sent to the scene.
</P>
<P>
"People have been conveyed to various hospitals in the region
due to the sheer numbers of injured," he said.
</P>
<P>
Inspector Peter Bruton, of Leicestershire Police, said senior
officers and were trying to investigate the cause of the serious
accident. 
